Benefits of K-Tip extensions 🖤

✔️ Natural appearance: Keratin tip hair extensions provide, by far, the most natural look and feel to your hair. 
✔️ No Salon Maintenance:The maintenance of K-tip extensions is easier than other types of hair extensions. Once they are installed, you don’t have to worry about them. Just take care of them like your natural hair.
✔️ Long- Lasting Results: with proper care K-tips may last between 4-5 months. 
✔️ Versatility: Waterproof 😅 You can style them like your natural hair! Allowing for a variety of hair styles!

Building a good clientele is not easy! Sometimes we must do more than what’s expected!

Let me give you my personal example. I normally don’t work at night. If I have a k-tip client I will normally take them in no later than 11am. K-tip installs are the appointments that take the longest.

My client is a Kindergarten teacher at a Catholic School and she doesn’t take days off. The only way she can make it to her hair appointment is after  school.  Her Saturdays are not available because she tutors additional students and she really needed her hair done this month because she’s attending her friends wedding next week. 

🫶🏻 So this is when our professional sympathy kicks in! I took her in yesterday for a late appointment and got home around 10pm. 🌛

My kids go to a private Catholic school and I also attended a private Catholic school all my life! I know that world and how it is. 

I understand her availability and appreciate the hard work that she puts in everyday dealing with kindergartners. 😅 

My toddler makes me want to pull my hair out sometimes. Can’t imagine dealing with 30 little ones at once! 😳 

Anyhow! We must help out our teacher clients! They’re heroes by helping us educate our children as we hustle everyday! 

Thank you teachers for all your help! 🙏🏻 ♥️ 

Share with a teacher! Tell them thank you! 🫶🏻

Julie suffered from a chemical cut this past June. Leaving her in complete depression. 

She asked for help to 15 other Hair extensions specialists & was denied time after time. She completely gave up on trying all these months.

She reached out to me last week and asked me for help. I knew this was no easy peasy job and it was going to be very challenging. 

 I knew that if I didn’t help her this beautiful woman was going to hide under a beanie for the holidays! 

I said “yes” and took the challenge! 

🌼  @hairbydaisyroxx  First colored her hair with a level 5 to even it out and make it solid! 

After 9 Hours , 300 K-Tip Bonds, Combline on crown area, Endless Stories and life confessions Julie walked out feeling like a new woman! Her hair is not perfect but its 100 times better than what she originally had! She now has hair that falls down on both sides of her face! 

This season is about giving not only stuffing out faces with food 🥘 

Happy Thanksgiving Everyone🍁

My 🧠 is constantly thinking of 100 things at once and most of the time I don’t even know how I made certain things happen especially when you’re a mommy of two young kids, wife, business owner and the oldest sister of 4. 

Take a glimpse of the thoughts that hit my brain all at once the moment I get up in the morning. 🌤️
(Giselle’s Brain) 
-Need to get new socks for Nate
-Need to make my insurance payment
-Damn, I didn’t make it to Costco again
-Need to prep that clients hair
-I forgot to order more Wipes on Amazon
